  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a copper pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the ground pork and cook until browned, stirring frequently.",
    "Stir in paprika, garlic powder, salt, and pepper, cooking for one minute.",
    "Add the reconstituted low‑carb spaghetti and mix until coated with the pork mixture.",
    "Pour in the sour cream, stirring until the sauce thickens and coats the spaghetti.",
    "Transfer the pasta to a copper mug, sprinkling grated cheddar on top.",
    "Place the mug on a low‑heat setting to melt the cheese until bubbly.",
    "Deep‑fry the frozen onion rings in a small pan until golden and sprinkle over the pasta before serving."
